  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">In the system of equations above, <span class=\"italic\">a</span>&nbsp;is a constant. If the system of equations has no solution, what is the value&nbsp;of&nbsp;<span class=\"italic\">a</span>&nbsp;?</p>\n",
